      <title>阿里巴巴与万事达卡推出美国联名商业信用卡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-05/alibaba-com-mastercard-launch-us-co-branded-business-credit-card</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里巴巴宣布与万事达卡和 Cardless 合作推出联名信用卡，旨在奖励企业（尤其是中小型企业）进行跨境和国内采购。阿里巴巴总裁张阔与彭博社的 Scarlet Fu 谈论阿里巴巴商业优势信用卡，这是该公司首张联名美国信用卡。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-05/alibaba-com-mastercard-launch-us-co-branded-business-credit-card</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 18:21:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
