      <title>选举前市政债券销售额将飙升至四年来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/muni-debt-sales-set-to-surge-to-four-year-high-ahead-of-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[各州和地方政府准备以四年来最快的速度出售债务，因为借款人希望应对 11 月美国总统大选可能带来的波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/muni-debt-sales-set-to-surge-to-four-year-high-ahead-of-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 18:07:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
